---

<Layout title="About">
  <main class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6">
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] md:gap-20">
      <InfoBox class="relative top-0 h-fit flex-col items-center gap-8 md:sticky md:top-[10%]">
        <img src="/illustration.webp" alt="Profile" class="max-h-[30vh]" />
        <div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text!">Sparsh Kaushik</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-medium">Full Stack Developer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4"></div>
      </InfoBox>
      <div class="resume">
        <div class="text-2xl font-medium text-text mt-8 mb-4 first:mt-0">About Me</div>
        <p class="text-base font-normal">
          I'm a Full Stack Developer who builds web and mobile applications
          that scale. Currently at Newsa, I work across the stack with
          TypeScript, Next.js, React Native, and Supabase to ship products used
          by real people every day.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base font-normal mt-4">
          My journey includes building Manthan, an ERP system serving 8,000+
          users at VIPS-TC, developing AI-powered platforms at Sortin, and
          creating IoT dashboards for wildlife conservation at Nightjar. I'm
          comfortable with React, Svelte, Node.js and I handle everything from database design to deployment. I love Bun BTW.
        </p>
        <div class="text-2xl font-medium text-text mt-8 mb-4">Experience</div>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4">
          <span class="text-[1.1rem] font-medium">Jul 2025 – Current</span>
          <span class="text-[1.15rem] font-medium text-accent">Software Engineer</span>
          <span class="text-base font-normal">Newsa (Hybrid) Gurugram, Haryana, India</span>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-12 mt-2">
            <li>
              Building newsa.in web and mobile applications, developing
              responsive user interfaces and cross-platform mobile experiences.
            </li>
            <li>
              Technologies: TypeScript, NextJS, Expo, React Native, Tailwind
              CSS, Supabase, Legend State.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4">
          <span class="text-[1.1rem] font-medium">Jan 2025 – Jul 2025</span>
          <span class="text-[1.15rem] font-medium text-accent">Software Engineer (Intern)</span>
          <span class="text-base font-normal">Sortin (Hybrid) Gurugram, Haryana, India</span>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-12 mt-2">
            <li>
              Engineered the frontend, integrated APIs, and optimized AI model
              prompts for newsa.sortin.in, enabling the platform to collate
              results from diverse sources via natural language user queries.
            </li>
            <li>
              Technologies: TypeScript, NextJS, Tailwind CSS, React Query,
              Supabase, Zustand.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4">
          <span class="text-[1.1rem] font-medium">Jul 2024 – Aug 2024</span>
          <span class="text-[1.15rem] font-medium text-accent">Software Engineer (Intern)</span>
          <span class="text-base font-normal"
            >Nightjar Technologies (Hybrid) Gurugram, Haryana, India</span
          >
          <ul class="list-disc pl-12 mt-2">
            <li>
              Developed and implemented a responsive web application and mobile
              app for Trailguard AI, featuring sections like analytics
              dashboards, real-time camera feed, battery monitoring, and
              notification management.
            </li>
            <li>
              Integrated complex API functionalities to ensure seamless
              communication between the Frontend and Backend, enhancing the
              app's performance and user experience.
            </li>
            <li>
              Technologies: Typescript, NextJS, Expo, React Native, Tailwind
              CSS, Axios, REST API.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4">
          <span class="text-[1.1rem] font-medium">Nov 2022 – Dec 2024</span>
          <span class="text-[1.15rem] font-medium text-accent">Full Stack Engineer - erp.vips.edu</span>
          <span class="text-base font-normal"
            >Vivekananda Institute of Professional Studies Delhi, India</span
          >
          <ul class="list-disc pl-12 mt-2">
            <li>
              Developed and deployed "Manthan," an in-house ERP system for
              VIPS-TC College, supporting over 8,000 users with modules for
              event management, faculty attendance, and an LMS for student
              activities.
            </li>
            <li>
              Integrated biometric hardware for accurate faculty attendance
              tracking, ensuring precise and efficient record-keeping.
            </li>
            <li>
              Provided multi-platform access through a web app, Android app, and
              an admin dashboard, enhancing user accessibility and operational
              efficiency.
            </li>
            <li>
              Technologies: React, Typescript, SCSS, NextJS, React Native,
              Firebase.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4">
          <span class="text-[1.1rem] font-medium">Jul 2023 – Nov 2023</span>
          <span class="text-[1.15rem] font-medium text-accent">Frontend Engineer</span>
          <span class="text-base font-normal">Freelance Remote</span>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-12 mt-2">
            <li>
              Developed and customized a responsive SvelteKit analytics
              dashboard with interactive graphs, tailored to client needs for
              optimized data visualization and decision-making.
            </li>
            <li>
              Technologies: Typescript, SvelteKit, Tailwind CSS, REST API.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="text-2xl font-medium text-text mt-8 mb-4">Education</div>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4">
          <span class="text-[1.1rem] font-medium">2021 - 2025</span>
          <span class="text-[1.15rem] font-medium text-accent">B.Tech. AIML</span>
          <span class="text-base font-normal">VIPS-TC</span>
          <p class="text-text mt-2">
            Graduated with a Bachelor of Technology in Computer Science and
            Engineering from VIPS-TC, where I was a member of the C.O.D.E.
            technical society and the college's ERP Team.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4">
          <span class="text-[1.1rem] font-medium">2021</span>
          <span class="text-[1.15rem] font-medium text-accent">SECONDARY SCHOOL</span>
          <span class="text-base font-normal">Delhi International Public School</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-2xl font-medium text-text mt-8 mb-4">Technologies</div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(100px,1fr))] gap-4">
          {
            technologies.map((tech) => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <Icon name={tech.icon} class="w-8 h-8" />
                {tech.name}
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
